# Claude Code Configuration

# Project-specific settings for Claude Code development

## Project Type
project_type: quantconnect_trading

## Language Settings
primary_language: python
python_version: 3.8+

## Code Style
max_line_length: 100
use_type_hints: true
docstring_style: google

## Testing
test_framework: pytest
min_coverage: 80

## Development Preferences
- Prioritize code clarity over cleverness
- Always add docstrings to new functions/classes
- Include error handling for data access
- Log important trading decisions
- Use descriptive variable names
- Comment complex trading logic

## File Organization
- Keep algorithms under 300 lines (extract to modules if larger)
- One algorithm per file
- Group related utilities together
- Separate concerns: strategy, execution, risk management
